🔬 ForensicQuizzer – Learn Forensics On The Go

ForensicQuizzer is an iOS-based mobile application that enables users to practice quizzes related to various branches of forensic science. It provides immediate feedback along with detailed scientific explanations for every answer.

---

📱 Features

- Subject-wise quiz categories (e.g., Toxicology, Entomology, Serology)
- Detailed answer explanations
- Clean and intuitive UI for iPhone users
- Offline access (upcoming)
- Performance tracking and history (upcoming)

